| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0769 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomed)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: edaeeb19-58f1-5bf1-8a38-7cb07d22cd56"
